msgid ""
"The VC Directory buffer also defines some single-key shortcuts for VC "
"commands with the @kbd{C-x v} prefix: @kbd{=}, @kbd{+}, @kbd{l}, @kbd{i}, "
"@kbd{D}, @kbd{L}, @kbd{G}, @kbd{I}, @kbd{O}, and @kbd{v}."
